<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">The duration of food and drink is no longer a fixed number based on quality but based on the number of combines required to make the recipe as well as its quality.
<br />

<br />
The bonus effect of food and drink is capped by your Adventurer level.  If you are a 10th level Enchanter and drink a 40th level drink, your power regeneration rate will be as if you drank a 10th level drink, not a 40th level one.</span><span class="gensmall"><br /><br />Last edited by Provender on Mon Jan 24, 2005 2:11 pm; edited 1 time in total</span></td>
</td></tr>
