<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">Tier 1 drinks include jum jum juice, black coffee, and white tea.  All tier 1 drinks are level 10 (good for 1-10).
<br />

<br />
Tier 2 drinks include orange juice, antonican coffee, black tea, and wheat malted milk.  All tier 2 drinks are level 20 (good for 1-20).
<br />

<br />
Tier 3 drinks include fayberry juice, mountain coffee, oolong tea, and rye malted milk.  All tier 3 drinks are level 30 (good for 1-30).
<br />

<br />
Be sure to examine the food and drink before buying it.  Some provisions can last up to 5 hours while other drinks barely last longer than the 30 minutes you can get from NPC-sold provisions.
<br />

<br />
Food is particularly nice for non-Summoner Mages (like Enchanters!) who can cannibalize for power.</span><span class="gensmall"><br /><br />Last edited by Provender on Mon Jan 24, 2005 2:14 pm; edited 3 times in total</span></td>
</td></tr>
